dcterms:description: A multimodal dataset comprising anonymized patient records containing 865,275 text, 428,391 images, 421,785 videos, and 463,814 audio for training, with 1,000 text, 1,000 images, 1,000 videos, and 1,000 audio for evaluation.
dcterms:title: Multimodal dataset comprising anonymized patient records

dcterms:description: A large-scale medical question-and-answer dialogue dataset used for pre-training the medical language module to improve understanding of medical terminology.
dcterms:title: Large-scale medical question-and-answer dialogue dataset

dcterms:description: A dataset of real-world medical cases used for evaluating the performance of the Stone Needle framework, consisting of multimodal input data including text, images, videos, and audio.
dcterms:title: Real-world medical cases dataset
